{"tid":1060323,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手半年 仲未放底 有咩方法可以放低前度","createTime":"2019-03-13T16:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T03:38:21.000Z","uid":180178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1721dc7883d4176d5fad067bc53338a4059f51c7","tid":1060323,"uid":180178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T16:53:07.000Z","msg":"同ex係初戀 拍左四年拖 <br />\n散左半個月後佢已經有新男朋友 <br />\n但係我到而家都仲未放得低<br />\n我曾經令自己好憎佢 以為可以藉此忘記佢 但係原來根本做唔到 <br />\n甚至因爲咁而傷害左另一個中意我嘅人<br />\n呢排仲要日日都夢見佢 嚴重過分手嗰一排<br />\n有冇方法可以令我放低佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開錯台 開多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e25260cc22f45dba7189b71fe2dc32cc127ae9b","tid":1060323,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T16:54:49.000Z","msg":"一陣你放閪低佢就好撚無面架下"},{"pid":"36b966df79cc556ec2187305f37a34ea0c52748f","tid":1060323,"uid":180178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e25260cc22f45dba7189b71fe2dc32cc127ae9b","tid":1060323,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T16:54:49.000Z","msg":"一陣你放閪低佢就好撚無面架下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T17:00:53.000Z","msg":"有冇面根本唔係重點 重點係成個人都好似逃離唔到佢咁"},{"pid":"6bf0e0cf3a8e41027a6977f92820a79fa471dc9e","tid":1060323,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36b966df79cc556ec2187305f37a34ea0c52748f","tid":1060323,"uid":180178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e25260cc22f45dba7189b71fe2dc32cc127ae9b","tid":1060323,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T16:54:49.000Z","msg":"一陣你放閪低佢就好撚無面架下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T17:00:53.000Z","msg":"有冇面根本唔係重點 重點係成個人都好似逃離唔到佢咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T17:01:33.000Z","msg":"Sorry 你咁認真"},{"pid":"41a5cd89e7b86347f2cb7850e2222b43c5dd53c0","tid":1060323,"uid":180178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T17:03:29.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以救下我<